00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,080
It is raining now!

877
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:01,920
It started out of expectation indeed.

878
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:41,720
Report!

879
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,320
Most people of Xinguan Village

880
00:32:43,520 --> 00:32:44,440
have evacuated towards Nanyang Town.

881
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,720
But a critically-ill patient

882
00:32:45,840 --> 00:32:46,600
is having an operation.

883
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:47,760
Two special policemen

884
00:32:47,840 --> 00:32:48,600
and five medical personnel

885
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:49,240
are still in Xinguan Village.

886
00:32:49,480 --> 00:32:50,080
A8 asks

887
00:32:50,320 --> 00:32:51,040
if it is possible

888
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:52,320
to delay the flood discharging time.

889
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:57,280
Ask them

890
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:58,720
how long it will take
