00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:07,000
and arrived at the safe place.

903
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,480
Notify them

904
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:14,440
to start blasting.

905
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:15,480
Yes.

906
00:34:17,460 --> 00:34:22,340
(Nanyang Town)

907
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:58,800
Take care. Take care.

908
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:00,840
Take care.

909
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,520
Come on, comrades, take care.

910
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:02,840
I am sorry.

911
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:05,000
Okay, take care.

912
00:35:05,680 --> 00:35:06,840
Take care.

913
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:10,880
Xia, I will go there and check first.

914
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:11,880
Okay.

915
00:35:19,560 --> 00:35:21,120
You are fully soaked on this side.

916
00:35:21,640 --> 00:35:22,160
Dry it.

917
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:23,320
No. I am too dirty all over.

918
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,480
Your scarf will be polluted.

919
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:26,600
It doesn’t matter. Just dry it.

920
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,680
Okay, thanks!

921
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:34,440
In the evening
when you gave me the biscuits…

922
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:35,160
Captain Shu, Captain Shu,

923
00:35:35,680 --> 00:35:36,400
someone called

924
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,560
and claimed to have found

925
00:35:37,560 --> 00:35:38,080
Zhang Guihua’s husband.

926
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:39,600
Got it. Where is he?

927
00:35:40,080 --> 00:35:41,240
He has been delivered to the temporary

928
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:42,120
rescue station at Mingyue Village.

929
00:35:42,680 --> 00:35:43,840
Okay, I will get there soon.

930
00:35:44,240 --> 00:35:44,790
Mingyue Village shouldn’t

931
00:35:44,820 --> 00:35:45,320
be far from here, right?

932
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:45,860
Let’s go.

933
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:46,600
Go.

934
00:35:46,640 --> 00:35:47,600
Come on. Give me the key.

935
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:08,620
