936
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:10,370
All materials are in place.

937
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,960
Just have a good rest.

938
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:14,840
You don’t need to worry about others.

939
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:33,080
Is there a new task?

940
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,240
The miners have been trapped

941
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,120
