942
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:37,360
I will go and check it with them.

943
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,520
Mr. Shao.

944
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:48,800
How are things going on now?

945
00:36:49,560 --> 00:36:51,200
Five to six victims

946
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:52,000
are in a bad condition.

947
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:53,800
I must rush them back to the base camp

948
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,360
for further treatment.

949
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,360
The mine

950
00:36:58,640 --> 00:36:59,840
has some miners trapped

951
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:00,840
for a few days

952
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:01,880
and doctors are needed there.

953
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:05,480
I want to go there with Captain Xing.

954
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:09,600
Just go there with Dr. Lin.

955
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:10,360
It is enough for me to

956
00:37:10,520 --> 00:37:11,400
deliver the victims back alone.

957
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,810
Okay.

958
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:14,720
Mr. Shao, I will arrange the car

959
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:15,480
to deliver you back first.

960
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:16,400
Thanks!

961
00:37:16,680 --> 00:37:17,680
Take good care of her.

962
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:33,600
Dear,

963
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:36,320
where have you been?

964
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:38,400
Why did you come back so late?

965
00:37:38,640 --> 00:37:40,280
You really made me so worried.

966
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:42,520
Come on, have a look.

967
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:43,800
I… I…

968
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:45,760
I bought

969
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:48,760
your favorite apples for you.

970
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,960
You… Why are you crying?

971
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:53,680
I am happy.

972
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:55,840
Who made you unhappy?

973
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,440
I am happy.

974
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:59,960
You should smile if you are happy.

975
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:02,000
Just smile.

976
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:05,080
I enjoy your smiles.

977
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,880
You look so pretty in smiles.

978
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:09,080
I will smile.

979
00:38:10,640 --> 00:38:11,960
This apple

980
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:13,840
is big and red.

981
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:16,200
Just take it to your office tomorrow.

982
00:38:17,520 --> 00:38:19,440
I will certainly take it with me.

983
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:22,960
Come back earlier next time.

984
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:25,880
I am hungry.

985
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:28,720
Okay. Okay.

986
00:38:33,640 --> 00:38:34,880
It feels so great

987
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:36,000
to grow old

988
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:37,840
hand in hand like this.

989
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:52,960
Is it here?

990
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:54,160
Yes, here.

991
00:39:02,080 --> 00:39:02,800
Come on, madam.

992
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:04,080
Take care!

993
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,000
Come on, sir!

994
00:39:06,280 --> 00:39:06,840
-Take care.
-Xia.

995
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:07,760
Xia.

996
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:09,050
Find a settlement for them.

997
00:39:09,100 --> 00:39:10,200
-Okay.
-I must go to the command office.

998
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:10,840
-Okay.

999
00:39:10,850 --> 00:39:11,620
-Madam.
-Sir.

1000
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:12,600
Please wait for me.

1001
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:13,920
-Wait.
-Madam.

1002
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:14,520
Come on, madam!

1003
00:39:15,460 --> 00:39:16,410
Take care.

1004
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:18,920
-Take care.
-Okay.

1005
00:39:18,920 --> 00:39:20,500
(Earthquake Relief)

1006
00:39:27,560 --> 00:39:28,800
Zhang, have a good rest.

1007
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:29,760
We are here.

1008
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:31,440
Keyao!

1009
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,240
You have done a good job.

1010
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:34,880
But you’d better be stronger

1011
00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:36,360
if you come to rescue next time.

1012
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:37,360
Cover it.

1013
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:38,560
Thanks!

1014
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:39,560
You will be okay after the sleep.

1015
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:41,960
You are still here.

1016
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:43,960
Haven’t gone back?

1017
00:39:46,720 --> 00:39:47,560
What’s up? Caught a cold?

1018
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:48,600
I may have caught a cold

1019
00:39:48,680 --> 00:39:49,760
on the way back.

1020
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:51,680
Shall I prepare some medicines for you?

1021
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:53,280
Okay, thanks!

1022
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:11,400
Take it as it is still hot.

1023
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:12,720
Mr. Shao.

1024
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:13,920
A patient has a very poor condition.

1025
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:14,680
Please go and check it.

1026
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,240
Okay, I will be there right away.

1027
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:31,960
Shu Wenbo.

1028
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,200
What’s up?

1029
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:46,440
You were soaked in water just now.

1030
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:49,880
Ginger tea, to dispel cold.

1031
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:51,920
Thank you!

1032
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:56,000
Drink it as it is still warm.

1033
00:40:56,240 --> 00:40:57,160
It doesn’t work if it is cold.

1034
00:40:57,520 --> 00:40:58,480
Okay.

1035
00:41:05,200 --> 00:41:06,200
Thanks!

1036
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:10,720
Have you found a settlement for them?

1037
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:11,920
Yes.

1038
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,720
They are having a rest now.

1039
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:16,280
Just now, her husband insisted on

1040
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:17,640
eating oil-covered noodles

1041
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:18,920
like a child.

1042
00:41:19,200 --> 00:41:20,360
Nobody could comfort him.

1043
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:21,840
She settled the problem

1044
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:23,640
in just two minutes.

1045
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,760
How do you think about it?

1046
00:41:26,120 --> 00:41:28,520
Love is really a very strange thing

1047
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:31,000
as the lover is just your inborn master.

1048
00:41:32,680 --> 00:41:33,840
Her husband forgot

1049
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:35,520
many things and people

1050
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:36,240
after he fell ill.

1051
00:41:36,680 --> 00:41:37,560
He only remembers

1052
00:41:37,640 --> 00:41:38,800
his lover is Zhang Guihua.

1053
00:41:39,240 --> 00:41:40,360
The people of the rescue station

1054
00:41:40,600 --> 00:41:41,880
of Mingyue Village told me

1055
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:42,560
he had said to all people

1056
00:41:43,200 --> 00:41:44,040
his wife is Zhang Guihua

1057
00:41:44,120 --> 00:41:45,280
before I arrived.

1058
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:46,880
He kept looking for her.

1059
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,680
Even if he forgets the whole world,

1060
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:53,040
he can’t forget his lover.

1061
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:56,120
Exactly!

1062
00:41:58,760 --> 00:41:59,920
Sit down.

1063
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,520
Okay.

1064
00:42:09,120 --> 00:42:10,040
I have a question for you.

1065
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:11,080
Go ahead.

1066
00:42:11,520 --> 00:42:12,480
What did you say

1067
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:13,520
that night

1068
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:14,800
when you delivered biscuits to me?

1069
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:19,280
I was wearing earphones and editing

1070
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:21,000
the video clips and heard nothing.

1071
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:23,000
I raised my head
and found you were away.

1072
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:25,400
I see.

1073
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,200
What on earth did you say then?

1074
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:28,520
I went there

1075
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:29,360
to say sorry to you.

1076
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:30,640
I thought you had refused to talk to me

1077
00:42:31,040 --> 00:42:32,200
because you were angry.

1078
00:42:32,560 --> 00:42:33,800
And then you left?

1079
00:42:34,080 --> 00:42:34,960
Er…

1080
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:36,520
You weren’t sincere at all

1081
00:42:36,560 --> 00:42:38,440
to apologize to me.

1082
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:39,720
Listen,

1083
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:41,280
I will give you another chance.

1084
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:42,880
Do it again.

1085
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:48,560
Ruan Qingxia,

1086
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,320
I was too arbitrary previously

1087
00:42:50,680 --> 00:42:51,440
and misunderstood you.

1088
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:53,480
The rescue work

1089
00:42:54,280 --> 00:42:55,760
proves your real abilities.

1090
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:57,840
I am so sorry.

1091
00:42:58,240 --> 00:42:59,880
Today, I will apologize to you formally.

1092
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:01,760
I am sorry.

1093
00:43:02,800 --> 00:43:04,840
I will accept your apology.

