♪Watching the stories of others♪

1099
00:43:44,680 --> 00:43:50,600
♪And wondering
Who will conquer my heart♪

1100
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:55,640
♪Because of an incident♪

1101
00:43:56,320 --> 00:43:59,600
♪My life has changed♪

1102
00:44:00,160 --> 00:44:05,040
♪It’s true that from now on♪

1103
