♪I won’t harm anyone♪

1104
00:44:12,240 --> 00:44:15,480
♪I won’t have any regrets♪

1105
00:44:15,960 --> 00:44:21,760
♪Yet by the casual twist of fate♪

1106
00:44:24,000 --> 00:44:27,520
♪All beautiful imaginations♪

1107
00:44:27,720 --> 00:44:30,720
♪Have become real in a sudden♪

1108
00:44:31,600 --> 00:44:37,240
♪It seems I do have
