1114
00:45:02,520 --> 00:45:05,400
♪And thus my life changed♪

1115
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:10,960
♪It’s true that from now on♪

1116
00:45:13,760 --> 00:45:17,240
♪I know what is hope♪

1117
