00:45:48,880 --> 00:45:51,920
♪How should I make you
Feel safe with it♪

1125
00:45:52,560 --> 00:45:59,640
♪I hope I’m the one you can count on
Do you think the same as me♪

1126
00:46:06,080 --> 00:46:09,920
♪Love by accident
Yet it’s more than an accident♪

1127
00:46:10,200 --> 00:46:13,440
♪Love indeed exists♪

1128
00:46:13,960 --> 00:46:19,800
♪I think you’re free to love♪

